ximately the last  years in which energy was very cheap he believes that this bubble is coming to an end he has stated his opposition to the keystone pipeline on the basis of the ruinous environmental consequences that its construction will bring to alberta and to the entire planet due to the contribution that burning the extracted oil would make to climate change philanthropyedit grantham together with his wife hannelore established the grantham foundation for the protection of the environment in  substantial commitments have been made to imperial college london the london school of economics and the university of sheffield to establish the grantham institute  climate change and environment the grantham research institute on climate change and the environment and the grantham centre for sustainable futures respectively which will enable the institutions to build on their extensive expertise in climate change research the  tax filing for the grantham foundation for the protection of the environment shows the foundation donated  million to both the sierra club and to nature conservancy and  million to the environmental defense fund that year the foundation has also provided support to greenpeace the wwf and the smithsonian from  the grantham foundation for protection of the environment funded a  prize for environmental reporting the prize was administered by the university of rhode islands metcalf institute for marine  environmental reporting awards and honoursedit this list is incomplete you can help by expanding it grantham was appointed commander of the order of the british empire cbe in the  birthday honours for philanthropic service to climate change research  honorary degree imperial college london  honorary degree the new school new york  honorary degree the university of sheffield referencesedit  gmo llc official site accessed february    a b charlie rose show interview with jeremy grantham accessed may    paul b farrell  december  obamas predictably irration