ovides its services to high net worth individuals investment companies pooled investment vehicles pension and profit sharing plans charitable organizations corporations state or municipal government entities and other investment advisers it manages separate clientfocused equity fixed income balanced and multi portfolios the firm also launches and manages equity fixed income balanced mutual funds and hedge funds for its clients it invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe the firm also invests in commodities and currencies markets it invests in derivatives grantham mayo van otterloo  co llc is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor the firm provides its services to high net worth individuals investment companies pooled investment vehicles pension and profit sharing plans charitable organizations corporations state or municipal government entities and other investment advisers it manages separate clientfocused equity fixed income balanced and multi portfolios the firm also launches and manages equity fixed income balanced mutual funds and hedge funds for its clients it invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe the firm also invests in commodities and currencies markets it invests in derivatives as well for the equity portion of its portfolio the firm typically makes its investments in value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations for the fixed income portfion of its portfolio it invests in diversified portfolio of investments including sovereign and quasisovereign debt instruments assetbacked securities government bonds and us and nonus fixed income securities it employs absolute return and longshort strategies to make its investment the firm employs fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolio it benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the citigroup indices barclays indices jp morgan indices msci indices and sp indices the firm invests in natural resources sector it conducts inhouse research to make its investments grantham mayo van otterloo  co was founded in  and is based in boston massachusetts with an additional offices in berkeley california and san francisco california detailed description  rowes wharfboston ma united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwgmocom key executives for grantham mayo van otterloo  co llc mr bradley jay hilsabeck chief executive officer partner and member of board of directors mr eijk alexander de mol van otterloo cofounder senior portfolio manager and director age  dr paul woolley phd chairman of gmo uk mr jeanpierre mittaz chief operating officer ms melissa spurlock head trader of equity compensation as of fiscal year  grantham mayo van otterloo  co llc key developments gmo presents at morningstar investment conference chicago  apr  am apr   gmo presents at morningstar investment conference chicago  apr  am venue hyatt regency mccormick place  south dr martin luther king jr drive chicago il  illinois united states speakers catherine legraw grantham mayo van otterloo  co llc announces executive changes effective february   jan   grantham mayo van otterloo  co llc announced that scott hayward former ceo of quantitative management associates llc qma will take the helm of gmo as ceo effective february   replacing peg mcgetrick current ceo on an interim basis who will remain a director of the firm hayward spent  years at qma including  as ceo he previously held executive positions at jennison associates and jpmorgan mcgetrick also announced the hiring of andy martin from cambridge associates ca to fill a newly created role head of investment teams martin spent  years with ca most recently as managing director in the nonprofit practice and global head of hedge fund research grantham mayo van otterloo  co lays off  of workforce jun   grantham mayo van otterloo  co has laid off approximately  of its  employees worldwide grantham mayo van otterloo  co layoffs including how many bostonbased personnel are affect