  research group prior barclays global investors na portfolio manager prior   axa rosenberg investment management llc axa rosenberg investment management provides investment management services based on fundamental equity analysis using quantitative methods the firms investment approach is driven by bottomup stock selection based on the rigorous fundamental analysis of company valuations and earnings combined with an understanding of both the stock specific and environmental risks that accompany this approach axa rosenberg’s approach is applied globally and is implemented locally by experienced investment teams based in the us europe and asia to create broadly diversified portfolios with a range of objectives from active equities including enhanced index large cap small cap and “defensive equity income” type strategies and smartbeta strategies the firm primarily invests in common stocks traded on the principal exchanges of major markets the use of derivatives is currently not a strategic part of their investment approach however their goal is to be fully invested in equities at all times as permitted axa rosenberg may use stock index futures or etfs to overlay cash or accruals and obtain exposure to the equity markets investment strategist prior blackrock fund advisors blackrock fund advisors offers active enhanced and index strategies across markets and asset classes the firms products are offered in a variety of structures including separate accounts mutual funds ishares etfs and other pooled investment vehicles blackrock fund advisors also offers risk management advisory and enterprise investment system services to institutional investors through blackrock solutions nonprofit donations  grants     the chest foundation the chest foundations mission is to provide resources to advance the prevention and treatment of diseases of the chest awards  honors professional certification cfa chartered financial analyst sponsored by cfa institute other affiliations binu georg